channel.title: 742 Entitylist Error
channel.description: so i get this error when someone kills one of either the godwars bosses or occasionaly other bosses (not always!) i get this error wile the server is running, even when i shut the server down with eclipse and start it back up it dosnt show it in the command box as an error, until someone goes and kills one of those bosses. [IMG]http://www.upload.ee/image/4271855/entity_error.PNG[/img] [IMG]http://www.upload.ee/image/4271862/enetity_list_2.PNG[/img] I have lost my mind (Damn near) looking for what the problem could possibly be, i know its not my entity class because even replacing it did the same thing, it could be something to do with the spawining. as for that im clueless as to what it is, This is vital because once this error pops up, the npcs spawn slow/ or not at all. could someone please help?
